text: Pogonocherus ehdenensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Sama and Rapuzzi in 2000. It is known from Lebanon.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus ehdenensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 2000
